### CB6 Quantum — API Test File (REST Client)
### Usage: Click "Send Request" above any request block
### Set variables in .vscode/settings.json → rest-client.environmentVariables

# ── Fyers ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Fyers: Get Profile
GET https://api.fyers.in/api/v3/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv ACCESS_TOKEN}}

###

### Fyers: NIFTY Quote
GET https://api.fyers.in/data-rest/v2/quotes/?symbols=NSE:NIFTY50-FUT
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv ACCESS_TOKEN}}

###

### Fyers: BANKNIFTY Quote
GET https://api.fyers.in/data-rest/v2/quotes/?symbols=NSE:NIFTYBANK-FUT
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv ACCESS_TOKEN}}

###

### Fyers: FINNIFTY Historical (15min, last 5 days)
GET https://api.fyers.in/data-rest/v2/history/?symbol=NSE:FINNIFTY-FUT&resolution=15&date_format=1&range_from=2026-06-01&range_to=2026-06-04&cont_flag=1
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv ACCESS_TOKEN}}

###

# ── IIFL Capital ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### IIFL: Profile (verify token is live)
GET https://api.iiflcapital.com/v1/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv IIFL_USER_SESSION}}

###

### IIFL: Trading Limits
GET https://api.iiflcapital.com/v1/limits
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv IIFL_USER_SESSION}}

###

### IIFL: Open Orders
GET https://api.iiflcapital.com/v1/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv IIFL_USER_SESSION}}

###

### IIFL: Positions
GET https://api.iiflcapital.com/v1/positions
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv IIFL_USER_SESSION}}

###

# ── TrueData ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### TrueData: Auth (get session token)
POST https://api.truedata.in/users/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username={{$dotenv TRUEDATA_USER}}&password={{$dotenv TRUEDATA_PASSWORD}}

###
